Package: nflpredict
Title: NFL Game Prediction Model - Multi-Sport Blueprint
Version: 2.7.2
Authors@R: person("Data Analyst", email = "analyst@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive NFL game prediction model using Monte Carlo simulation,
    Gaussian copula correlation, spline calibration, and Kelly staking.
    Features include strength-of-schedule adjustments, injury impact modeling,
    weather effects, and professional-grade betting analytics.
    Designed as a blueprint for multi-sport prediction models.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
